-## Troubleshooting
+## VS Code 配置
+
+仓库保留了 Isaac Lab 模板中的 VS Code 环境配置工具。可以在 VS Code 中运行任务 `setup_python_env`，按提示填写 Isaac Sim 安装路径。生成的 `.vscode/.python.env` 会帮助 Pylance 索引 Isaac Sim、Omniverse 和 Isaac Lab 的扩展路径。
+
+## 常见问题
+
+### 找不到任务
+
+先确认扩展已安装：
+
+```bash
+python -m pip install -e source/delto_walnut_hcy
+```
+
+再运行：
+
+```bash
+python scripts/list_envs.py
+```
+
+如果修改过任务名，确认 `scripts/list_envs.py` 中的筛选字符串仍能匹配新的任务名。
 
-### Pylance Missing Indexing of Extensions
+### 找不到 Isaac Lab / Isaac Sim 模块
 
-In some VsCode versions, the indexing of part of the extensions is missing.
-In this case, add the path to your extension in `.vscode/settings.json` under the key `"python.analysis.extraPaths"`.
+说明当前 `python` 不是 Isaac Lab 对应的解释器。请切换到安装 Isaac Lab 的 conda/venv，或使用：
 
-```json
-{
-    "python.analysis.extraPaths": [
-        "<path-to-ext-repo>/source/delto_walnut_hcy"
-    ]
-}
+```bash
+/path/to/IsaacLab/isaaclab.sh -p scripts/rsl_rl/train.py --task Template-Delto-Walnut-Direct-v0 --headless
 ```
 
-### Pylance Crash
+### GPU 显存不足
+
+降低并行环境数量：
+
+```bash
+python scripts/rsl_rl/train.py --task Template-Delto-Walnut-Direct-v0 --num_envs 128 --headless
+```
+
+### 训练结果没有按预期收敛
+
+优先检查这些位置：
 
-If you encounter a crash in `pylance`, it is probable that too many files are indexed and you run out of memory.
-A possible solution is to exclude some of omniverse packages that are not used in your project.
-To do so, modify `.vscode/settings.json` and comment out packages under the key `"python.analysis.extraPaths"`
-Some examples of packages that can likely be excluded are:
+- `delto_walnut_hcy_env_cfg.py` 中的 `action_scale`、`decimation`、`episode_length_s`。
+- `delto_walnut_hcy_env.py` 中 `_get_rewards()` 的各项 reward 权重和日志。
+- `rsl_rl_ppo_cfg.py` 中的学习率、网络规模、`num_steps_per_env` 和 `max_iterations`。
 
-```json
-"<path-to-isaac-sim>/extscache/omni.anim.*"         // Animation packages
-"<path-to-isaac-sim>/extscache/omni.kit.*"          // Kit UI tools
-"<path-to-isaac-sim>/extscache/omni.graph.*"        // Graph UI tools
-"<path-to-isaac-sim>/extscache/omni.services.*"     // Services tools
-...
-```
\ No newline at end of file
+训练时可关注日志中的 `r_rot`、`r_sym`、`r_tan`、`r_axis`、`r_dropped`、`r_smooth`、`r_omega`、`r_torque`、`r_collision` 和 `total_reward`。
